== Concert repertoire ==
''The following is a small selection'':

=== Operatic arias ===
Ivan Susanin from ''Life for the Tsar'' by [[Mikhail Glinka|Glinka]]; King Rene from ''Iolanta'' by [[Pyotr Ilyich Tchaikovsky|Tchaikovsky]]; Song of the Varangian Guest from ''Sadko'' by [[Nikolai Rimsky-Korsakov|Rimsky-Korsakov]]; King Philip  from ''Don Carlos'' by [[Giuseppe Verdi|Verdi]]; Konchak from ''Prince Igor'' by [[Alexander Borodin|Borodin]]; The Old-Man<U+2019>s Tale from ''Aleko'' by [[Sergei Rachmaninoff|Rachmaninov]]; Kutuzov from ''War and Peace'' by [[Sergei Prokofiev|Prokofiev]]; Serenade of Mefistofeles from ''Faust'' by [[Charles Gounod|Gounod]], Song of the Flea by [[Modest Mussorgsky|Mussorgsky]].<ref name="Arias">{{cite web|url=http://www.leonidharitonov.ru/music|title=Singer Leonid Kharitonov|last=Kharitonov|first=Mikhail Leonidovich|work=Music page|language=Russian|accessdate=2009-10-17}}</ref>

